00:09:02.569 --> 00:09:06.990
with much of the ground fighting taking place
in jungles. Rather than large-scale offensives,

00:09:06.990 --> 00:09:11.329
troops were sent on search and destroy missions
and often it was difficult to tell enemy from

00:09:11.329 --> 00:09:16.170
civilians. Capturing territory wasn’t meaningful,
