In addition to jungle fighting, there was
a lot of bombing. Like, more bombs were dropped

00:09:24.110 --> 00:09:30.819
on North and South Vietnam than both the Axis
and Allied powers used in all of World War

00:09:30.819 --> 00:09:34.350
II. The U.S. used chemical defoliants like
Agent Orange to get rid of that pesky jungle,

00:09:34.350 --> 00:09:38.430
and also napalm, which was used to burn trees,
homes, and people.

00:09:38.430 --> 00:09:42.180
Television coverage meant that Vietnam was
the first war brought into American living

00:09:42.180 --> 00:09:46.250
rooms. And people were horrified at what they
